Resource Profile: Profile on AccessAuditTrailEvent for CH ATC

Official URL: http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-epr-fhir/StructureDefinition/AccessAuditTrailEvent Version: 5.0.0-ballot
Active as of 2018-05-28 Computable Name: AccessAuditTrailEvent

Copyright/Legal: CC0-1.0

This profile defines the content of the access audit trail event which a community has to provide for a patients audit trail.

Usage:

  • Use this Resource Profile: ChAtcIti81Response
  • Examples for this Resource Profile: AuditEvent/atc-log-read
  • CapabilityStatements using this Resource Profile: CapabilityStatement for the Patient Audit Record Repository
